de: Auch 1,5 km: Véronique und Serge begrüßen Sie in einem großen Haus aus dem 19. en: Auch at 1,5 km : Véronique and Serge welcome you in a large house of the XIXth century, with a breathtaking view on the castles and the countryside, located at the doors of Auch (Cathedral, Museums).the very comfortable and spacious rooms have a contemporary decoration, each one with shower-room and separate toilet, TV, mini-bar, desk. You can relax in the spa and sauna (free). On site: camping in farmhouse and leisure cottages, swimming pool with whirlpool, spa, sauna, lake, fishing, pedal boats. Free internet access. parking. On the first floor: 2 bedrooms with 1 bed 160, 1 bed 90, shower room/wc, 1 bedroom with 3 beds 90, shower room/wc, 1 bedroom with 1 bed 160, 2 beds 90, shower room/wc, living room. On the ground floor a large kitchen with fireplace, a dining room with fireplace. Services offered: Washing machine, baby bed, wall-mounted hair dryer. TV in each room, hot drinks kit, desk, mini-bar.
